---
interface Props {
  stateAgencyAbbreviation: string;
}

const { stateAgencyAbbreviation } = Astro.props;
---

<aside
  class="my-12 rounded-lg border border-disclaimer-border bg-disclaimer-bg/40 p-6"
  aria-labelledby="reassurance-heading"
>
  <h2 id="reassurance-heading" class="!mt-0">Why this isn't a scam — what we don't do</h2>
  <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
    <li>
      <strong>We don't contact your parent or family.</strong> We never collect their name, income, Social Security
      number, or any personal information.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>We don't sell your email address.</strong> Ever. Not to attorneys, not to Medicaid planners, not to
      lead-generation companies. (<a href="/privacy">Read the privacy policy.</a>)
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>We're not a Medicaid planner, attorney, or referral site.</strong> We don't get paid kickbacks for sending
      you anywhere.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Every claim on this page cites a {stateAgencyAbbreviation} document.</strong> If you find anything that
      doesn't match what {stateAgencyAbbreviation} publishes, tell us and we'll fix it.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Money back if {stateAgencyAbbreviation} rejects your QIT</strong> for any reason traceable to this guide.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>You stay in control of the trust.</strong> Your family's trustee manages the bank account; we never touch
      your parent's money.
    </li>
  </ul>
</aside>
